## âš¡ Quick Start
### Local Mode
```python
from zaicore import ZAICore

ai = ZAICore()
ai.learn("mission", "to build adaptive AI frameworks")
ai.recall("mission")
```

### Remote Mode
```python
ai = ZAICore(remote_mode=True, remote_url="https://example.com/zai_core_api")
ai.learn("language", "Python")
```

